extends layout

block content
  .container 
    .heading-section.mb-5
      .heading-text
        h1 Explore
        p Take a tour to our store and find exotic tastes of coffee. Find yourself suitable coffee machine form world's best producers.
      .circle1 
      .circle2 
      .circle3

  .home-section
    .home-section-text.text-center
      h3.text-uppercase Check our special offers
      p.text-muted Or contact us to get personalized offer and discounts.
      .home-section-buttons 
        a.button-main(href="/special-offers") Check special offers 
        a.button-secondary(href="/special-offers") Contact us

    .home-section-cards.container
      .row 
        .col-3 
          .card
            .card-body
              h4.card-title Services
              p.card-text
                | Broken machine? No worries! We can fix this.
                | Our store repairs broken coffee machines and
                | keeps working ones in good condition. Our experienced 
                | service workers will take care of your machine with 
                | best practices and in short time, so you don't run 
                | out of coffee!
              a.card-link(href='/services') Discover services
        .col-3 
          .card
            .card-body
              h4.card-title Premium machines
              p.card-text
                | Our store offer the best coffee machines in the world.
                | We sell brands like:
                br
                | - Phillips 
                br
                | - Kurps 
                br
                | - Delonghi 
                br
                | - Saeco
              a.card-link(href='/expresses') Explore machines
        .col-3 
          .card
            .card-body
              h4.card-title Discounts
              p.card-text
                | Subscribe to our newsletter to be up to date with 
                | our incoming discounts. We run weekly -50% sales on 
                | the most popular coffee types, so you better don't 
                | miss this event!
              a.card-link(href='/special-offers') Check discounts
        .col-3 
          .card
            .card-body
              h4.card-title Fast delivery
              p.card-text
                | ExpressShop offer one of the fastest deliveries. You'll 
                | get your desired coffee or machine in under 24 hours! 
                | You can order a mobile service to your location if you 
                | are unable to bring your machine to one of our service 
                | points!
              a.card-link(href='/contact') Contact us now